cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the problem of detecting and recognizing traffic signs using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes improvements in the detection and recognition pipeline, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as well. The application of the proposed approach is in traffic-sign inventory management, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
